I represent Rabbi Dovid Gottlieb, Rabbi of Congregation Shomrei Emunah in Baltimore, Maryland. I write to advise you of an infringement of copyrighted work belonging to Rabbi Gottlieb, and to request that Google, Inc. remove or disable access to such material.
